{
  "stem": "19923.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And as best as I can recollect, that was before 1936 when-- when Cologne was part of the occupied territory, or had been occupied by the-- the French and the English after the Armistice of World War I.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was, I think, demilitatized.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Hitler walked into the Rhineland in 1936, and nobody stopped him.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "After he walked into the Rhineland, that's when the antisemitism in Cologne started.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So I have some recollections of life-- what life was like at an earlier time when the persecution of the Jews was not as severe as it was after Hitler walked into the Rhineland.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And so I had a contrast in terms of what-- what, in my earliest recollections, what it was to live without too much antisemitism and what it was like to live with it on a daily basis.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So I-- I wanted to bring that to your attention to show you that, even as a child, I have memories that go back to age three and four in Germany.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They didn't have to say anything.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You-- you knew.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You knew what was going on just from conversations, from listening to the radio.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When Hitler talked, they had loudspeakers on every street, and you could hear what he was saying.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so, you know, you-- you could listen to the conversation.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And you can hear his virile, I mean, antisemitic tirades on the radio, and it would make you shrink, cringe, the way he talked.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it's not something that had to be verbally discussed.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Everybody knew.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And you didn't have to be an adult.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You could be a child and be aware of the hatred.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And perhaps that's a kind word.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It's more than hatred.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It's a virulent antisemitism which causes people to cringe.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
